{"tid":1656780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教你點簡單check隻手機app係咪支那野","createTime":"2019-10-15T18:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:33:25.000Z","uid":158977,"like":131,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8c887220ddaeb4e6c52d075abc36ba552510a8c6","tid":1656780,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"講明先 唔係支那野唔代表唔會send野上支那 所以use apps at your own risk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下步驟iOS/An都適用 步驟差少少 但大致相同<br />\n<br />\n1 去你想查嘅嗰隻app嘅play store/app store版面 佢會有個位係about this app/ 關於此應用程式<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbxMv5A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbxMv5A.png&h=08d1b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2 然後你會見到個公司名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZoXwHcU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoXwHcU.png&h=ecb7cebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3 之後好簡單咁將個公司名拎去Google search<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFxgTog.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFxgTog.png&h=dc83a9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4 最後你會發現好多人用嘅photogrid原來係支那野<br />\n<br />\n*********<br />\n如果你google search之後冇直接彈佢公司資料出嚟 咁你就去佢公司個網度 換contact us/聯絡我們之類嘅野 <br />\n<br />\n我用snow嚟做<strong>例子</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRefpuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRefpuA.png&h=f47d6d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會見到佢公司地址喺泡菜 可以<strong>放心少少</strong> 因為仲未fc有冇奶共 呢啲要靠其他巴打慢慢針佢啲條款細則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢間cheetah mobile同埋嗰間fancy mobile apps都係支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最鍾意出埋啲咩咩一鍵清垃圾嘅app呃鳩啲廢老/唔識手機嘅人download <br />\n一鳩野將啲資料send曬上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話就話清咗好多位比你 其實你去返手機設定睇 佢係冇多到位<br />\n<br />\n諗下都知 點會次次都清到成GB出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊得嚟咁多垃圾 要清垃圾就用Google files go啦 Google出㗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以</span></span> 如果你見到你老豆老母有裝呢啲野 快啲del撚咗佢 <br />\n我因為工作需要 成日都會接觸中年/老人家電話 佢地好多都有裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Check清楚先好download野！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"95a8bc80c55b1ae0f360c76bdf008f62e50ffd62","tid":1656780,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f3aeaa5a846ab31ffc3280a4705bcd48d3190b69","tid":1656780,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2035db170b1fe547a56a99ef52dddee68f207370","tid":1656780,"uid":67237,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"原來snow唔係大陸嘢？<br />\n不過用app影自己個樣都係覺得好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eeae9bbc01e8427125ddb4fa046482f29ab7f9","tid":1656780,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"仆街 PhotoGrid 支那㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇替代推介？"},{"pid":"df016b0e4a63b5bf97683d33f9204360ba77f83b","tid":1656780,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除